    {
      "id": "minimum-content-template-contract",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Contract Note",
      "position": {
        "x": 680,
        "y": 20
      },
      "width": 600,
      "height": 620,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Minimum Content Node Contract\n\nThis template is the smallest class-backed authored node that still behaves correctly in the browser and editor.\n\n## Required Parts\n\n- `title`: frames the node for humans.\n- `type-definition`: declares the node's semantic type and authority.\n- `node-view`: defines the on-canvas surface.\n- `editor-view`: defines the bottom-panel edit surface.\n- `markdown`: optional note/example content for the authoring graph itself.\n\n## Expected Content Shape\n\nA minimal content node usually carries:\n\n- `label`\n- one primary payload field such as `data.markdown`, `data.text`, or `data.html`\n\n## Render Shape\n\nThe node view should declare rendering explicitly instead of inferring it from field names alone.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"view\": {\n    \"intent\": \"node\",\n    \"payload\": \"render.markdown\",\n    \"renderShape\": {\n      \"kind\": \"markdown\",\n      \"sourcePath\": \"data.render.markdown\",\n      \"renderRole\": \"node\",\n      \"presentationProfile\": \"markdown.default\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Editor Shape\n\nThe editor view should expose at least:\n\n- `label`\n- the primary content field\n\nThat is enough to give the node a real Edit button and a working bottom editor panel.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node"
        },
        "_bridge": {
          "sourceBridgeNodeId": "minimum-content-template-markdown-port",
          "sourceBridgeLabel": "Markdown",
          "targetKind": "node-class",
          "classKey": "markdown",
          "classRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node"
        },
        "definitionKey": "markdown"
      }
    }
  ],
